summer vacation.

00:50:20.300 --> 00:50:22.900
And immediately, the people's
rational, that's when I did my

00:50:22.900 --> 00:50:26.550
most like creative stuff, really
self-directed things.

00:50:26.550 --> 00:50:28.300
Those are my best memories
from childhood.

00:50:28.300 --> 00:50:31.090
